    <div class="Assessment.name">Room Sizes</div>
    <div class="im_statement"><p>A house has a kitchen, a playroom, and a dining room on the first floor. The areas of the kitchen, playroom, and dining room in square feet are in the ratio <span class="math math-repaired">\(4 : 3 : 2\)</span>. The combined area of these three rooms is 189 square feet. What is the area of each room?</p>
